  <section class="intro">
   <div class="container">
     <div class="row">
       <div class="twelve columns text-center">
         <h1>Your WordPress project just got a lot more productive</h1>
       </div>
       <div class="ten offset-by-one columns text-center">
         <p>Communicate with your clients and team. <b><i>All in one place.</i></b> The Mercury messenger app is a widget that is docked to your web browser when you are logged in as a WordPress admin. Anyone who visits your project will not see the messenger app, but anyone who is logged in has the ability to message and send data to single user or group  on their respective project.</p>
       </div>
     </div>
   </div>
