       <div class="four columns text-center">
         <p><i class="fa fa-smile-o fa-5x"></i></p>
         <h3>Convenient Messaging</h3> <p class="text-left">Communicate immediately with team members and clients, just send a quick message. Now it is native on your WordPress website.</p>
       </div>
       <div class="four columns text-center">
         <p><i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-5x"></i></p>
         <h3>Work Directly with Clients</h3><p class="text-left"> Web Developers can manage all of their clients needs and requests neatly and efficiently. Need to communicate immediately just send a quick message.</p>
       </div>
     </div>
   </div>
