       <h1>Why Mercury? It's Simple</h1>
       <p > Mercury was made to increase productivity for content managers and website managers. Email and other productivity apps can be clunky and corporate. The Mercury Messenger App is active only to admins and is a simple way to commmunicate with your team and clients.<h3>All in one place.</h3>
       </p>
       <p>
         <i class="fa fa-coffee fa-4x"></i>
