<section id="features">
 <div class="container">
   <div class="row">
     <div class="twelve columns text-center">
       <h1>Full of great features and benefits</h1>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
 <div class="container">
   <div class="row">
     <div class="four columns">
       <li><b>SSL-encryption.</b> Conversations stay safe and sound.</li>
       <li><b>Multi-browser support.</b> From Firefox to Windows, Safari and Chrome.</li>
       <li><b>Group messages.</b> Message single users or message as many groups as you want.</li>
       <li><b>Conversation history.</b> Admins and users have access to all past messages.</li>
     </div>
     <div class="four columns">
       <li><b>Profile image ready.</b> Personalize with a profile image and add personality to your team.</li>
       <li><b>Emoji support.</b> What would messaging be without emoji support ;)</li>
       <li><b>Username enabled.</b> Create a unique username so you can be easily discovered.</li>
       <li><b>Cloud dashboard.</b> Admins and users have access to cloud based home screen to view all of their projects in one convenient place.</li>
       <li><b>Mobile friendly.</b> Mobile enabled to give you access on the go.</li>
     </div>
     <div class="four columns">
       <li><b>Easy onboarding.</b> Mercury App makes project management and team organization extremely effective.</li>
       <li><b>Quick referencing.</b> Read back through you messages to find tasks, instruction and approvals.</li>
       <li><b>Fast approvals.</b> Admins and users can quickly communicate with clients and each other.</li>
       <li><b>Clean task management.</b> Communicate and create with your team all within your own website.</li>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</section>
